</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Peter Bernus</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p><b>Peter Bernus</b> (born 1949) is an Hungarian Australian scientist and Associate Professor of <a href="/wiki/Enterprise_Architecture" title="Enterprise Architecture" class="mw-redirect">Enterprise Architecture</a> at the School of Information and Communication Technology, <a href="/wiki/Griffith_University" title="Griffith University">Griffith University</a>, Brisbane, Australia.<sup id="cite_ref-IFAC08_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IFAC08-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
<div id="toctitle">
